quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,De fast gallopers
  100,2,Igniting sparks
  100,3,Invading enemy morning
  100,4,Striking terror therein
  100,5,Penetrating heart their territory
  100,6,human est est unappreciative de his Dominus
  100,7,He bears testis hoc fact
  100,8,He loves material things excessively
  100,9,he non realize ut feria advenit when graves perfecit opened
  100,10,Totus secrets est brought out
  100,11,"They perfecit invenit out, ut feria their Dominus est fully Cognizant de them"